narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Crystal Colone is a Physician Assistant provider based in Norco, CA. From 2018-01 through 2018-11, this provider received $83K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 1K beneficiaries, billing 2 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 86% of billing is concentrated in 99213 (99213), indicating significant specialization in this service.
Billing stopped in 2018-11, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
